                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2606.19930/2606.19930v1/images/case-study/case-study-good-latex.png",
                "caption": "Figure 7:Case study on AndroidWorldExpenseDeleteMultiple2.The task asks the agent to delete three expenses from Pro Expense: Streaming Services, Unexpected Expenses, and Pet Supplies. The baseQwen3-VL-8Bloses the task flow after an early deletion and gets stuck around the menu/sidebar. The adaptedForgeQwen3-8Bfollows the task-specific deletion workflow and removes all requested expenses.",
