                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2606.19930/2606.19930v1/x1.png",
                "caption": "Figure 8:AndroidWorld tag-wise failure-rate reduction.Each cell reports the reduction in attempt-level failure rate afterMobileForgeadaptation relative to the corresponding base agent; higher is better. Blue cells indicate fewer failures after adaptation, while orange cells indicate regressions.",
